<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> عبد الله بن حميد<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> عبد المجيد حسن<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> إبراهيم بن محمد آل الشيخ<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
